{"race_list":["HUMAN","ELF","HALFLING","DWARF","YEEK","GIANT","UNDEAD","ORC","YETI","MINOTAURUNDEAD"],"races":{"DWARF":{"desc":"<p>矮人是一支隐秘的种族，生活于地下世界钢铁王座。<\/p><p>他们是支强壮的种族并以大师级手艺而闻名，但是，由于在过去的战乱中为了自身利益抛弃了其他种族，他们仍然不受欢迎。<\/p><p>矮人们出于对金钱的热衷和他们对王国的热爱而联合在一起。<\/p>","display_name":"矮人","name":"Dwarf","short_name":"DWARF","subrace_list":["DWARF","DREM"]},"ELF":{"desc":"<p>精灵这个名字通常被用来不正确地称呼整个精灵种族。<\/p><p>精灵分为 3 个相互联系的种族，而目前只有两种还幸存着。<\/p><p>除了永恒精灵用魔法保持永生，其他精灵通常能活一千年。<\/p><p>在不同的精灵种族之间他们对世界的看法很不相同。<\/p>","display_name":"精灵","name":"Elf","short_name":"ELF","subrace_list":["SHALORE","THALORE","DOOMELF"]},"GIANT":{"desc":"<p><span style=\"font-style: italic\"><span class=\"tstr-font-italic\">\"巨人\"<\/span><\/span> 是对那些身高超过八英尺的人型生物的统称。他们的起源、文化和关系与其他种族迥异。他们被其他矮小的种族视为威胁而躲避，作为避难的流浪者而生存。<\/p>","display_name":"巨人","locked_desc":"庞然的巨物傲视着渺小的生灵。然而须知，高处不胜寒，站得越高，跌得越惨……","name":"Giant","short_name":"GIANT","subrace_list":["OGRE","KROG"]},"HALFLING":{"desc":"<p>半身人是一个身材十分矮小的种族，高度很少有超过 4 英尺。<\/p><p>只要愿意，他们可以像人类一样做到任何事情，并且更有纪律，更擅长学习。<\/p><p>半身人军队曾经征服了很多国家，并且在厄流纪时他们可以和人类联合王国制衡。<\/p><p>半身人身手敏捷，好运，但缺少力量。<\/p>","display_name":"半身人","name":"Halfling","short_name":"HALFLING","subrace_list":["HALFLING"]},"HUMAN":{"desc":"<p>人类与半身人一起是马基·埃亚尔的主要种族，他们曾互相争战了几千年，直到在领袖们的伟大领导下，人类和半身人的国度再度联合起来。<\/p><p>联合王国的人们已经保持了一个世纪的和平。<\/p><p>人类被分为两个亚种：高等人类和普通人类。高等人类体内流淌着魔法的血液，他们拥有额外的属性和感知能力并更长寿。<\/p><p>其他人类天生有更强的学习能力，他们能做任何他们想做的事成为任何他们想成为的人。<\/p>","display_name":"人类","name":"Human","short_name":"HUMAN","subrace_list":["HIGHER","CORNAC"]},"MINOTAURUNDEAD":{"desc":"<p>不死族是被黑暗魔法复活的人形生物（人类，精灵，矮人…）。<\/p><p>不死族有多种形态，从食尸鬼、吸血鬼到巫妖。<\/p>","display_name":"不死族","locked_desc":"死亡的力量，恐惧的意志，这些肉体不会沉寂。国王去世，主人陨落，我们才是永生。","name":"MinotaurUndead","short_name":"MINOTAURUNDEAD","subrace_list":["WHITEHOOF"]},"ORC":{"desc":"<p>兽人拥有久远而悲伤的历史。他们是，而且被见证为多次试图统治埃亚尔世界的侵略性种族。<\/p><p>但是一年前，西方来的灾星消灭了四个部落。一百年前，图库纳国王消灭了马基埃亚尔本土的所有兽人。<\/p><p>兽人种族处于灭绝边际，仅仅一步之遥。<\/p><p>但他们意志强大，敢于直面任何磨难，来创造属于他们的未来！<\/p>","display_name":"兽人","name":"Orc","short_name":"ORC","subrace_list":["ORC"]},"UNDEAD":{"desc":"<p>不死族是被黑暗魔法复活的人形生物（人类，精灵，矮人…）。<\/p><p>不死族有多种形态，从食尸鬼、吸血鬼到巫妖。<\/p>","display_name":"不死族","locked_desc":"死亡的力量，恐惧的意志，这些肉体不会沉寂。国王去世，主人陨落，我们才是永生。","name":"Undead","short_name":"UNDEAD","subrace_list":["GHOUL","SKELETON"]},"YEEK":{"desc":"<p>夺心魔是一支神秘的矮小人形种族，生活于热带岛屿瑞尔。<\/p><p>他们的身体覆盖着白色的皮肤，他们奇怪的身材比例使他们看上去滑稽可笑。<\/p><p>尽管他们在马基·埃亚尔中几乎不曾人们被提到过，他们已经作为半身人王国纳格尔的奴隶存在了数个世纪。<\/p><p>他们在派尔纪获得了自由并在那个时候建立了维网——一个由他们灵能思维组成的网络。<\/p>","display_name":"夺心魔","locked_desc":"一个种族，一种思想，一种道路。我们的压抑终于要终结，而我们将继承埃亚尔，不要认为我们很柔弱，只有那些帮助我们的人才能见识到我们的力量。","name":"Yeek","short_name":"YEEK","subrace_list":["YEEK"]},"YETI":{"desc":"<p>雪人族具有强大的肉体。<\/p>","display_name":"雪人","locked_desc":"鼓舞精神，牺牲肉体，荣耀永存。","name":"Yeti","short_name":"YETI","subrace_list":["KRUK_YETI"]}},"subraces":{"CORNAC":{"copy":{"default_wilderness":["playerpop","allied"],"extra_generic_point_every":10,"extra_talent_point_every":10,"faction":"allied-kingdoms","life_rating":10,"moddable_tile":"human_#sex#","moddable_tile_base":"base_01.png","random_name_def":"cornac_#sex#","starting_intro":"cornac","starting_quest":"start-allied","starting_zone":"trollmire","subtype":"human","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>科纳克人是来自联合王国北部的普通人类。<\/p><p>人类天生适应性强，他们可以在出生时获得 1 点<span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 天赋解锁点 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\">（其他种族只能在10、20和34级时获得1点）。此外，出生时以及每10级时，他们可以获得额外1点<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">职业技能点和通用技能点<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"><\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +0 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 10<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 0%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"科纳克人","experience":1,"images":[],"name":"Cornac","short_name":"CORNAC","talents_types":[]},"DOOMELF":{"copy":{"_forbid_start_override":true,"ashes_urhrok_race_start_quest":"start-shaloren","default_wilderness":["zone-pop","angolwen-portal"],"faction":"shalore","life_rating":9,"moddable_tile":"elf_#sex#","moddable_tile_base":"demonic_01.png","random_name_def":"shalore_#sex#","random_name_max_syllables":4,"starting_intro":"ashes-urhrok","starting_quest":"ashes-urhrok+start-ashes","starting_zone":"ashes-urhrok+searing-halls","subtype":"elf","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>魔化精灵并不是一个真正的种族，他们曾是永恒精灵，而被恶魔抓去，变为末日的使者。<\/p><p>他们对折磨敌人感到享受。<\/p><p>他们具有<span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 加速 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能，能每隔一段时间让自己脱离相位空间。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -2 力量, +1 敏捷, +1 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +3 魔法, +2 意志, +0 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 9<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"魔化精灵","experience":1.12,"images":[{"file":"npc\/demon_statue_uruivellas-cropped.png","height":106,"width":61}],"locked_desc":"玛·洛克的恶魔绝不会对你施以祝福！ \n三者可以诉说精灵所带来的恐怖\n之一在无尽的深海中永远咆哮\n之一召集邪徒为复活另一者而战\n静默他们的声音，隐藏你的踪影\n新的精灵终将诞生…","name":"Doomelf","short_name":"DOOMELF","stats":{"con":1,"cun":0,"dex":1,"mag":3,"str":-2,"wil":2},"talents_types":{"race\/doomelf":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 魔化精灵"]}},"DREM":{"copy":{"_forbid_start_override":true,"calendar":"dwarf","cults_race_start_quest":"start-allied","default_wilderness":[20,17],"faction":"sanctuary-of-horrors","life_rating":12,"moddable_tile":"dwarf_#sex#","moddable_tile_base":"base_drem_01.png","random_name_def":"dwarf_#sex#","random_name_max_syllables":4,"starting_intro":"cults","starting_quest":"cults+start-cults","starting_zone":"cults+town-kroshkkur","subtype":"dwarf","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>德瑞姆是生存于地底深处的异变种，直到最近才发现具有思维能力的个体。他们仍生存于地底，认为他们不会被地上种族欢迎。<\/p><p>他们拥有 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">狂热<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 天赋，让他们能在短时间内无视冷却时间。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +3 力量, +1 敏捷, +1 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +2 魔法, -1 意志, +0 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"德瑞姆","experience":1.12,"images":[],"locked_desc":"无面，但不无心。","name":"Drem","short_name":"DREM","stats":{"con":1,"dex":1,"mag":2,"str":3,"wil":-1},"talents_types":{"race\/drem":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 德瑞姆"]}},"DWARF":{"copy":{"calendar":"dwarf","can_see_iron_council":1,"default_wilderness":["playerpop","dwarf"],"faction":"iron-throne","life_rating":14,"moddable_tile":"dwarf_#sex#","moddable_tile_ornament2":{"female":"braid_01","male":"beard_02"},"random_name_def":"dwarf_#sex#","starting_intro":"dwarf","starting_quest":"start-dwarf","starting_zone":"reknor-escape","subtype":"dwarf","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>矮人是一支隐秘的种族，生活于地下世界钢铁王座。<\/p><p>他们是支强壮的种族并以大师级手艺而闻名，但是，由于在过去的战乱中为了自身利益抛弃了其他种族，他们仍然不受欢迎。<\/p><p>他们天生掌握 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 钢筋铁骨 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\">，允许他们在短时间内提高护甲和抵抗。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +4 力量 , -2 敏捷 , +3 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -2 魔法 , +3 意志 , +0 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 14<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 0%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"矮人","images":[],"name":"Dwarf","short_name":"DWARF","stats":{"con":3,"dex":-2,"mag":-2,"str":4,"wil":3},"talents_types":{"race\/dwarf":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 矮人"]}},"GHOUL":{"copy":{"cut_immune":1,"default_wilderness":["playerpop","low-undead"],"fear_immune":1,"forbid_nature":1,"global_speed_base":0.8,"inscription_forbids":{"inscriptions\/infusions":true},"life_rating":14,"moddable_tile":"ghoul","moddable_tile_nude":1,"poison_immune":0.8,"starting_intro":"ghoul","starting_level":3,"starting_level_force_down":true,"starting_quest":"start-undead","starting_zone":"blighted-ruins","stun_immune":0.5,"subtype":"ghoul","true_undead":1,"type":"undead","undead":1},"desc":"<p>食尸鬼是不能说话、身体腐烂，不知疲倦的不死生物，适合成为战士。<\/p><p>他们天生有独特的 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 食尸鬼 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能和一系列不死系技能：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p>- 极高的毒素抗性<\/p><p>- 流血免疫<\/p><p>- 震慑抵抗<\/p><p>- 恐惧免疫<\/p><p>- 独有食尸鬼技能：定向跳跃，侵蚀和亡灵唾液<\/p><p>食尸鬼腐烂的身体同时使它比别的生物行动要慢一些。<\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +3 力量 , +1 敏捷 , +5 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +0 魔法 , -2 意志 , -2 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 14<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12%<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">速度惩罚:<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> -20%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"食尸鬼","experience":1.12,"images":[],"locked_desc":"动如磐石，撕咬如火，跟随主人，平定江山！","name":"Ghoul","short_name":"GHOUL","stats":{"con":5,"cun":-2,"dex":1,"mag":0,"str":3,"wil":-2},"talents_types":{"undead\/ghoul":[true,1.1,"亡灵 \/ 食尸鬼"]}},"HALFLING":{"copy":{"default_wilderness":["playerpop","allied"],"faction":"allied-kingdoms","life_rating":12,"moddable_tile":"halfling_#sex#","random_name_def":"halfling_#sex#","size_category":2,"starting_intro":"halfling","starting_quest":"start-allied","starting_zone":"trollmire","subtype":"halfling","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>半身人是一个身材十分矮小的种族，高度很少有超过 4 英尺。<\/p><p>只要愿意，他们可以像人类一样做到任何事情，并且更有纪律，更擅长学习。<\/p><p>半身人军队曾经征服了很多国家，并且在厄流纪时他们可以和人类联合王国制衡。<\/p><p>他们天生掌握 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 小不点的幸运 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能可以使他们在几个回合内提高暴击几率。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -3 力量 , +3 敏捷 , +1 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +3 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +5 幸运<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 10%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"半身人","experience":1.1,"images":[],"name":"Halfling","short_name":"HALFLING","size":"较小","stats":{"con":1,"cun":3,"dex":3,"lck":5,"str":-3},"talents_types":{"race\/halfling":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 半身人"]}},"HIGHER":{"copy":{"default_wilderness":["playerpop","allied"],"faction":"allied-kingdoms","life_rating":11,"moddable_tile":"human_#sex#","moddable_tile_base":"base_01.png","random_name_def":"higher_#sex#","starting_intro":"higher","starting_quest":"start-allied","starting_zone":"trollmire","subtype":"human","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>自厄流纪起，高等人类就是人类种族的一支特殊分支，他们的身体里潜藏着魔力。<\/p><p>为了保持血统的纯正，他们一般不和普通人类通婚。<\/p><p>他们天生掌握 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 高等人类之怒 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\">，允许他们在短时间内提高伤害和抵抗。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +1 力量 , +1 敏捷 , +0 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +1 魔法 , +1 意志 , +0 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 11<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 0%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"高等人类","images":[],"name":"Higher","short_name":"HIGHER","stats":{"dex":1,"mag":1,"str":1,"wil":1},"talents_types":{"race\/higher":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 高等人类"]}},"KROG":{"copy":{"default_wilderness":[24,14],"faction":"zigur","forbid_arcane":1,"life_rating":13,"moddable_tile":"ogre_#sex#","moddable_tile_base":"krog_base_01.png","moddable_tile_ornament":{"female":"krog_deco_braids_default","male":"krog_deco_beard_default"},"random_name_def":"thalore_#sex#","random_name_max_syllables":4,"size_category":4,"starting_intro":"krog","starting_quest":"start-allied","starting_zone":"ruins-kor-pul","subtype":"krog","type":"giant"},"desc":"<p>克罗格是从食人魔转变而来的种族。除去了身上的魔法符文，伊格兰斯使用自然纹身和龙血维持他们的生命。克罗格专注于反魔战争，似乎不了解也不关心其他事物。<\/p><p>他们拥有 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">自然之怒 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能，让他们能震慑敌人。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +3 力量, -1 敏捷, +2 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -2 魔法, +2 意志, +0 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 13<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 15%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"克罗格","experience":1.15,"images":[],"locked_desc":"曾为憎恶，现为武器。","name":"Krog","short_name":"KROG","size":"较大","stats":{"con":2,"dex":-1,"mag":-2,"str":3,"wil":2},"talents_types":{"race\/krog":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 克罗格"],"wild-gift\/antimagic":[true,1.2,"自然 \/ 反魔法"]}},"KRUK_YETI":{"copy":{"auto_id":100,"default_wilderness":["playerpop","yeti"],"faction":"kruk-pride","life_rating":13,"moddable_tile":"yeti","moddable_tile_head_underwear":"fur_head.png","moddable_tile_higher_underwear":"fur_body.png","moddable_tile_lower_underwear":"fur_legs.png","starting_intro":"orc-yeti","starting_quest":"orcs+start-orc","starting_zone":"orcs+vaporous-emporium","subtype":"yeti","type":"giant"},"desc":"<p>雪人族具有强大的肉体。通常，他们只是无知觉的野兽，但这种有所不同。<\/p><p>少数克鲁克部落的兽人掌握了灵能，让他们能操控雪人族的思维，并用自己的意志取代。<\/p><p>这样做的话，他们旧的知识将失去效力，必须重新开始，在这个过程中他们能获得强大力量。<\/p><p>他们拥有 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 寒冰之怒 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能，让他们能将敌人封在冰块中。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +5 力量, -3 敏捷, +4 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +0 魔法, +1 意志, -1 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 13<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"克鲁克雪人","experience":1.12,"images":[{"file":"npc\/giant_yeti_yeti-cropped.png","height":77,"width":64}],"locked_desc":"鼓舞精神，牺牲肉体，荣耀永存。","name":"Kruk Yeti","short_name":"KRUK_YETI","stats":{"con":4,"cun":-1,"dex":-3,"str":5,"wil":1},"talents_types":{"race\/yeti":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 雪人"]}},"LICH":{"desc":"<p><\/p>","display_name":"巫妖","images":[],"locked_desc":"你不应该看见这个！","name":"Lich","short_name":"LICH","talents_types":[]},"OGRE":{"copy":{"default_wilderness":["playerpop","shaloren"],"faction":"shalore","life_rating":13,"moddable_tile":"ogre_#sex#","random_name_def":"shalore_#sex#","random_name_max_syllables":4,"size_category":4,"starting_intro":"ogre","starting_quest":"start-shaloren","starting_zone":"scintillating-caves","subtype":"ogre","type":"giant"},"desc":"<p>食人魔是变种人类，在厄流纪被孔克雷夫作为工人和战士而制造。<\/p><p>符文给他们超过自然界限的强大力量，但他们对符文魔法的依赖使之成为猎魔行动绝佳的目标，而不得不依附于永恒精灵。<\/p><p>他们简单的喜好与直接的方式令他们获得了哑巴和野兽的蔑称，尽管他们在法术和符文上有惊人的亲和力。<\/p><p>他们拥有 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">怒火中烧 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能，能提供暴击几率和伤害，并提供震慑定身免疫。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +3 力量 , -1 敏捷 , +0 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +2 魔法 , -2 意志 , +2 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 13<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 15%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"食人魔","experience":1.15,"images":[{"file":"npc\/giant_ogre_ogre_guard-cropped.png","height":112,"width":64}],"locked_desc":"他们铸造于数千年的仇恨之中，\n为一场现在已经结束的战争而造。\n他们被遗忘的诞生地深埋于地下，\n那些隧道已经腐朽，无处寻觅。\n过去的窃贼失败了，但他们的数据将永远保存；\n要想找到他们，请寻找那些摆弄传送门的半身人……","name":"Ogre","short_name":"OGRE","size":"较大","stats":{"con":0,"cun":2,"dex":-1,"mag":2,"str":3,"wil":-2},"talents_types":{"race\/ogre":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 食人魔"]}},"ORC":{"copy":{"auto_id":100,"default_wilderness":["playerpop","orc"],"faction":"kruk-pride","life_rating":12,"moddable_tile":"orc_#sex#","starting_intro":"orc","starting_quest":"orcs+kruk-invasion","starting_zone":"orcs+town-kruk","subtype":"orc","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>兽人拥有久远而悲伤的历史。他们是，而且被见证为多次试图统治埃亚尔世界的侵略性种族。<\/p><p>但是一年前，西方来的灾星消灭了四个部落。一百年前，图库纳国王消灭了马基埃亚尔本土的所有兽人。<\/p><p>兽人种族处于灭绝边际，仅仅一步之遥。<\/p><p>但他们意志强大，敢于直面任何磨难，来创造属于他们的未来！<\/p><p>他们拥有 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">兽人之怒<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> ，让他们能在几回合内增加伤害。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +2 力量, +1 敏捷, +1 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -1 魔法, +1 意志, +1 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"兽人","experience":1.12,"images":[{"file":"npc\/humanoid_orc_orc_warrior.png"}],"name":"Orc","short_name":"ORC","stats":{"con":1,"cun":1,"dex":1,"mag":-1,"str":2,"wil":1},"talents_types":{"race\/orc":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 兽人"]}},"SHALORE":{"copy":{"default_wilderness":["playerpop","shaloren"],"faction":"shalore","life_rating":9,"moddable_tile":"elf_#sex#","moddable_tile_base":"base_01.png","moddable_tile_ornament":{"female":"braid_02"},"random_name_def":"shalore_#sex#","random_name_max_syllables":4,"starting_intro":"shalore","starting_quest":"start-shaloren","starting_zone":"scintillating-caves","subtype":"elf","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>永恒精灵与魔法世界有着很强的联系，曾一度出现过许多伟大的魔法师。<\/p><p>尽管如此，他们仍试图保持避世并隐藏他们的魔法能力。因为他们深深记得那一段血腥的历史——魔法大爆炸还有紧随其后的猎魔行动。<\/p><p>他们天生掌握 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 不朽的恩赐 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\">，允许他们在短时间内提高整体速度。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -2 力量 , +1 敏捷 , +0 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +2 魔法 , +3 意志 , +1 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 9<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 12%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"永恒精灵","experience":1.12,"images":[],"name":"Shalore","short_name":"SHALORE","stats":{"con":0,"cun":1,"dex":1,"mag":2,"str":-2,"wil":3},"talents_types":{"race\/shalore":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 永恒精灵"]}},"SKELETON":{"copy":{"blood_color":{"b":127,"g":127,"r":127},"cut_immune":1,"default_wilderness":["playerpop","low-undead"],"fear_immune":1,"forbid_nature":1,"inscription_forbids":{"inscriptions\/infusions":true},"life_rating":12,"moddable_tile":"skeleton","moddable_tile_nude":1,"no_breath":1,"poison_immune":1,"starting_intro":"skeleton","starting_level":3,"starting_level_force_down":true,"starting_quest":"start-undead","starting_zone":"blighted-ruins","subtype":"skeleton","true_undead":1,"type":"undead","undead":1},"desc":"<p>骷髅是由有灵性的骨头组成的强壮而敏捷的不死生物。<\/p><p>它们天生具有独特的 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 骷髅 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\"> 技能和一系列不死系技能：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p>- 毒素免疫<\/p><p>- 流血免疫<\/p><p>- 恐惧免疫<\/p><p>- 不需要呼吸<\/p><p>- 独特骷髅技能