#ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 15%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"白蹄","experience":1.15,"images":[{"file":"npc\/undead_minotaur_whitehoof_maulotaur-cropped.png","height":92,"width":63}],"locked_desc":"死亡的力量，恐惧的意志，这些肉体不会沉寂。国王去世，主人陨落，我们才是永生。","name":"Whitehoof","short_name":"WHITEHOOF","stats":{"con":2,"cun":1,"dex":-1,"mag":2,"str":3,"wil":-3},"talents_types":{"race\/whitehooves":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 白蹄"]}},"YEEK":{"copy":{"blood_color":{"b":227,"g":0,"r":0},"confusion_immune":0.35,"default_wilderness":["playerpop","yeek"],"faction":"the-way","life_rating":7,"max_air":200,"moddable_tile":"yeek","random_name_def":"yeek_#sex#","size_category":2,"starting_intro":"yeek","starting_quest":"start-yeek","starting_zone":"town-irkkk","subtype":"yeek","type":"humanoid"},"desc":"<p>夺心魔是一支神秘的种族，生活于热带岛屿瑞尔。<\/p><p>尽管他们在马基·埃亚尔中几乎不曾人们被提到过，他们已经作为半身人王国纳格尔的奴隶存在了数个世纪。<\/p><p>他们在派尔纪获得了自由并在那个时候建立了维网——一个由他们灵能思维组成的网络。<\/p><p>他们天生掌握 <span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 主导思维 <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-WHITE\">，允许他们在短时间内控制一个较弱生物的思维。当效果结束时，被控制目标死亡。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p>虽然夺心魔不是两栖生物，但他们天生对水有种特殊的亲和力，允许他们屏息更长时间。<\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 属性修正：<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * -3 力量 , -2 敏捷 , -5 体质<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> * +0 魔法 , +6 意志 , +4 灵巧<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\"> 每等级生命加值： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 7<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">经验惩罚： <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> -15%<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #ffd700\"><span class=\"tstr-color-GOLD\">混乱抗性:<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #51ddff\"><span class=\"tstr-color-LIGHT_BLUE\"> 35%<\/span><\/span><\/p>","display_name":"夺心魔","experience":0.85,"images":[],"locked_desc":"一个种族，一种思想，一种道路。我们的压抑终于要终结，而我们将继承埃亚尔，不要认为我们很柔弱，只有那些帮助我们的人才能见识到我们的力量。","name":"Yeek","short_name":"YEEK","size":"较小","stats":{"con":-5,"cun":4,"dex":-2,"mag":0,"str":-3,"wil":6},"talents_types":{"race\/yeek":[true,1,"种族技能 \/ 夺心魔"]}}}}